  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Project Manager, ACMV",
  "description": "<h2><u>Project Manager, ACMV</u></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsibilities:Lead the Project Team as a Project Manager to monitor and manage the project progression and work within the costing.<br>\nMonitor and supervise sub contractors’ work progression according to shop drawings, method statements, material and samples.<br>\nLiaise and work with relevant authorities, sub-contractors or clients on shop drawings, materials and samples.<br>\nReview and align Mechanical design drawings to ensure compliance with design specifications and guidelines.<br>\nKnowledge in Mechanical and able to identify discrepancies between Mechanical, structural, ID, architectural and client provisions.<br>\nManage and execute project as per the deadline.<br>\nAttend meetings with contractors to address issues and update progress.<br>\nStudy and review drawings and specifications for compliance.<br>\nAllocate work to technicians and ensure jobs are correctly and properly achieved within standards and SOP.<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Requirements:Degree in Mechanical Engineering with 10 years of relevant experience OR Diploma in Mechanical Engineering with 15 years of relevant experience.<br>\nGood working attitude with high level of professionalism and integrity.<br>\nAble to work independently and possess good interpersonal skills.<br>\nProficient in MS office and Microsoft Project.<br>\nCapable of leading a team and working under stress.<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><br></h2>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 5,
